column5: A couple months back I posted a few pics on the Extreme Angler website. Today it was announced that I won a St. Croix Mojo rod!!!  I am so stoked.  Thanks to the guys at Extreme, Karl and Mark.  Keep up the good work . Thanks again. Can't wait to use my new rod.
Congrats to you Cudz!   I certainly know that it won't go to waste on you.
Congrats Cudz thats a great prize  Rob
Great job man, I entered that contest yesterday for there next draw.
go buy a lotto ticket!   congrats
You should ask'em if they have a boat you could trade it for    Way to go man...can't wait to see the first "Mojo Report"
Boat is the next win.  Don't think the Extreme boys will give me one of theirs.  Lol! I need to win a boat in that salmon hunt. When I get the rod I will post a pic.  I am still stoked.  Woohoo!
Congrats!!! Where's the pic?? ?? ??  Last month I got second place for my video on Trophy Clips.
Woohoo, that's great.  Good for you!!!!!  Joey
It wasn't the photo of you with the Duran Duran hat and the pink golf shirt you posted from that old photo album was it???
LOL! No Rob, it wasn't but that pic does deserve a prize.
